features: 🚕【4K 3840x2160P Dash Cam Recording】This WiFi dash cam allows you to achieve 3840x2160P /30fps ultra HD resolution, records every detail on the road for you. 🚕【Car Camera with WiFi & APP Control】4K dashcam has built-in WiFi, allowing for easy connection to your smartphone via the "WitCam" mobile app (available for both iOS and Android), which allow you can watch and download your recorded videos and photos directly to your smartphone for instant sharing on social media, or save it for future viewing.【Please note: the dash cam with adhesive bracket, not support to suction cup】

🚕【4K Front Dash Cam with Super Night Vision】This car camera features Advanced sensor improves increase exposure automatically in dark situations allowing clear imaging in low light environments. The 6-layer glass lens and F2.0 large aperture ensures the clarity of images at night. It provides outstanding image quality with a broader field of vision even in the dim light, which is 4 times resolution of traditional 1080P dash cameras.

🚕【4K Dashcam with Compact Design】Front dash cam with boasts a compact and reliable design( size: 3.15x1.18x1.97inch LWH), dash cam 4K can be hidden behind the rearview mirror, ensuring it doesn't obstruct your vision while driving. which can assure your safety. Compared to other car camera dash cam models, this one has a simplified installation and set up with detailed instructions included, finish the installation in minutes even for a first time user.

🚕【Loop Recording & Evidence Protection】The dashcam supports loop recording. When the memory card is full, the WiFi dash cam will automatically overwrite the oldest video with the newest video and store it on the local micro SD card, no need manual deletion, and the emergency locks file video will not be overwrittening, so the locked video can be retained as evidence.

🚕【Built-in G-Sensor & Emergency Recording】The dash cam front equipped with the G-sensor, when a shock or collision is detected, the dash camera will lock the current video and prevent it from being overwritten, which can be used as strong evidence for insurance claims.

🚕【Support 24H Parking Monitor After Connected to Hardwire Kits】To achieve this function, an extra car accessory- hardwire kit is required. The Dash Cam Hardwire Kit(NOT included, purchase separately) is needed for this function.When your car is bumped or scratched in the parked position, the dash camera will automatically turn on, by monitoring for any incidents while away, and automatically recording, providing you with multi-scene requirement and a safe driving experience.

🚕【Dash Cam with Intelligent Voice Broadcast】The smart dash camera comes with 8 voice prompts, which helps you to know the current status of your car dash cam via voice broadcast. For example, "Recording Start, Recording Stop, Please connect WiFi", let you enjoy the era of intelligence.

🚕【Heat Resistant with Super Capacitor】This front dash cam has a built-in supercapacitor, Compared with other lithium battery dash cams, which can withstand extreme temperatures from -4°F to 149°F to avoid the risk of overheating, will not explode or burn even if short-circuited, and its Service life is twice that of lithium-ion batteries. Provide you clear and stable video at all times and you can enjoy your journey at ease.

🚕【64GB SD Card Included & Worry-free Warranty】The 4K dash cam can support max 128GB SD Card (64GB SD card included), you don't need to buy SD card separately, which can save your money. In Additiona, We provide a 2-year warranty and 24/7 hours of technical support if you have any questions about the car camera, please feel free to contact us.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent Compact Plug and Play Dash Cam
reviews.reviewText: I did a lot research on Dash Cams before I made my purchase. I realized that I did not want features I'd never need or use, nor did I want or need the LCD Screen showing me what was being recorded. I wanted a compact Dash Cam that did not obstruct my vision and was Plug and Play simple to use, but with high enough resolution to read license plates. I decided on this Dash Cam and I made a great choice. It comes with a 64 gig micro SD card already installed. Setup was fairly easy and straight forward. I installed the Dash Cam on the windshield right behind my rear view mirror and took my time hiding the power cable where the headliner meets the windshield upper trim and over to down the the support arm, then under the passenger glove box dash area to the central cigarette lighter 12v power outlet. From inside my Sonata, you can't see the Dash Cam or any wires at all. From the outside, you have to look really close to see the Dash Cam because it visually blends in with the rear view mirror right behind the cam. It's been installed for a week now and it works great. the recorded videos are viewed on my phone. I have an iPhone and the setup and operation of the Cam was problem free. When I start the car, a voice prompt tells me its working. When I stop and turn off my engine, a voice prompt tells me its shutting down. I have more piece of mind driving now that it is installed. My girlfriend and my buddy both want me to install the same Dash Cam in their vehicles. Maybe I did too good a job installing it in my car. LOLI highly recommend this Dash Cam if you're looking for compact, simple and high resolution.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Minimalistic design and slender body-great value!
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. This dash Cam offers high-resolution recording and comprehensive coverage for a reliable and safe driving experience. License plates are some what readable if paused and zoomed in but just like most dashcams, not the best. One of the standout features of this dash cam is its WiFi connectivity, allowing seamless connection to your smartphone via the mobile app. This feature enables you to watch and download recorded videos and photos directly to your phone. Also, no need to constantly update the date/time stamp like other dashcams as it pulls the information from your smartphone.With its compact design, the 4K dash cam can be conveniently hidden behind the rearview mirror without obstructing your vision. Installation is simplified, and users can easily set it up using the detailed instructions provided. However, wifi only works with the car charger and does not work when connected to a PC usb port. Night mode was briefly tested and captures surrounding traffic details.Comes with a 64gb SD card worth at least a 1/3 of the cost of the dashcam, which is a huge plus! Overall, tested the dash cam for 2 hours (gets warm in temperatures over 35 degrees C but nothing unexpected and has a supercapacitor so less prone to explosion) and it combines high-resolution recording, convenient smartphone connectivity, average night vision, and reliable functionality. Well worth the price if you are searching for a minimalistic design and specifically great in cars with smaller wind shields.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It gave me peace of mind after installation.
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the DashCam Pro, and I've been thoroughly impressed with its performance. This little device has exceeded my expectations in every way. The video quality is outstanding, capturing crisp and clear footage even in low-light conditions. It's like having a reliable witness on the road, providing me with peace of mind knowing that I have evidence in case of any unexpected incidents.Setting up the DashCam was a breeze, and the user-friendly interface makes it simple to navigate through the settings and recordings. The loop recording feature ensures that I never run out of storage space, and the automatic collision detection is a real lifesaver. I appreciate how seamlessly it integrates into my car's interior, without obstructing my view. Overall, the DashCam Pro has proven to be an invaluable addition to my daily commute, offering safety, security, and convenience all in one package.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Is a good dash cam
reviews.reviewText: So I liked this dash cam because is not as expensive but gets the work done. It can be annoying sometimes because every time I turn the car, it would say something and it can be annoying. But I liked how it records and that you can access through your phone. I have another dash cam that was more expensive, and this one kinda resembles it since it has the same functions. I highly recommend this dash cam if your car is not as expensive but still want to record in case of an accident. It is very affordable and decent quality. It already comes with a SD card, which is awesome! It is pretty easy to set up so no need to worry about that either :)
